SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile ~/.ca-bundle.crt

IMAPStore tony.ampomah.jw-gmail-remote
Account tony.ampomah.jw-gmail

MaildirStore tony.ampomah.jw-gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/.mail/tony.ampomah.jw@gmail.com/
Inbox ~/.mail/tony.ampomah.jw@gmail.com/Inbox

Channel tony.ampomah.jw-gmail
Far :tony.ampomah.jw-gmail-remote:
Near :tony.ampomah.jw-gmail-local:
